description: AutoEsiM: Table storing automated eNodeB Self-Organizing Network (SON) measurements for specific cells, including timestamps, location, cell identifiers, and data version information.  dateTime: Timestamp of the measurement; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3:  Ancillary identifier (currently appears constant); vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; AutoEsiM.userLabel: User-defined label (currently empty); AutoEsiM.autoEsiMId: Unique identifier for the specific automated SON measurement.
